'''Madih Belaïd''' (yavutse 1 Mutarama 1974), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Tunisiya|Tuniziya]] . Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa ''serivise za tereviziyo zizwi cyane na firime zirimo Naouret El Hawa'', ''Al Akaber'' na ''Allo'' . <ref name="cinematunisien">http://cinematunisien.com/2019/06/17/madih-belaid/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 1 Mutarama 1974 i Sousse, muri [[Tuniziya]]. Yashakanye n'umukinnyi w'amafirime ukomoka muri [[Tuniziya]] Rim Riahi aho abashakanye bafite abana batatu<ref>http://www.africine.org/personne/madih-belaid/14491</ref>.

== Umwuga ==
Yize ibijyanye no gukina amafilime mu kigo cya Maghrebian Institute of Cinema muri Tunis kuva 1994 kugeza 1997<ref>https://www.mosaiquefm.net/fr/actualite-mosaique-fm-tunisie/18451/madih-belaid-et-zahira-ben-ammar-invites-de-romdhane-show</ref>. Nyuma yo kwimenyereza umwuga mu majwi no kuyobora, yabaye umuyobozi wungirije ku mashusho menshi muri Tuniziya no mu mahanga kandi yitabira amahugurwa yo kwandika mu [[Bufaransa]], [[Ubudage]] na Maroc. <ref name="cinematunisien">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[http://cinematunisien.com/2019/06/17/madih-belaid/ "Madih Belaid: Director"]. cinematunisien<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">14 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> Muri 1996, yanditse kandi ayobora firime ngufi: ''Tout bouille rien ne bouge'' <ref>http://cinematunisien.com/2019/06/17/madih-belaid/</ref>. Yayoboye filime ye yo gutanga impamyabumenyi, ''Croix X'' muri 2006 , yakoze ''L'Ascenseur ya'' gatatu muri 2007 nyuma Allô muri 2008. <ref>http://africultures.com/personnes/?no=14491&utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=480</ref>

Muri 2014, yahawe igihembo cyo gukora neza ikinamico ya ''Naouret El Hawa'' muri Romdhane Awards yahawe na Mosaïque FM. <ref>http://archivev2.mosaiquefm.net/fr/index/a/ActuDetail/Element/40234-romdhane-awards-le-prix-de-meilleure-realisation-revient-a-naouret-lahwe</ref> Muri uwo mwaka, yagizwe umunyamuryango w’abacamanza ku nshuro ya kabiri iserukiramuco rya Les Nuits du court métrage Tunisien i Paris. <ref>https://maisondelatunisie.org/communique-de-presse-les-nuits-du-court-metrage-tunisien-12-et-13-decembre-2014-paris-2eme-edition-resultats-de-la-competition/</ref> Muri 2016, yatsindiye igihembo ''cyumuyobozi mwiza w'ikinamico Al Akaber'' muri Romdhane Awards. <ref>https://www.mosaiquefm.net/fr/actualite-culturel-tunisie/19699/romdhane-awards-le-meilleur-realisateur-est-madih-belaid</ref>

